    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>At 7th level, you can quickly assist an ally in the chaos of battle. You gain a new reaction based on your Leadership Style:</p>\n<h3><strong>Esoteric Leadership</strong></h3>\n<p>You gain the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-warlord.warlord.Item.7D41MltcT2l6FOT2]{Magical Defense} reaction.</p>\n<h3>Imposing Leadership</h3>\n<p>You gain the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-warlord.warlord.Item.bZXRiXvkZugWQlap]{Harrowing Interruption} reaction.</p>\n<h3>Inspiring Leadership</h3>\n<p>You gain the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-warlord.warlord.Item.rbtJ32f5TracBkIz]{Courageous Defiance} reaction.</p>\n<h3>Skirmishing Leadership</h3>\n<p>You gain the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-warlord.warlord.Item.IvwlpksVyqXt6GOp]{Guerilla Tactics} reaction.</p>\n<h3>Tactical Leadership</h3>\n<p>You gain the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-warlord.warlord.Item.6jIyks4I1rUcTMDd]{Adjusted Strike} reaction.</p>"
